      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/2/1/75",
      "text": [
        " :\n\"كَانَ أَمِيرُ اَلْمُؤْمِنِينَ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ يَحْتَطِبُ وَ يَسْتَقِي وَ يَكْنُسُ وَ كَانَتْ فَاطِمَةُ عَلَيْهَا اَلسَّلاَمُ تَطْحَنُ وَ تَعْجِنُ وَ تَخْبِزُ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3640 - Hisham ibn Salim narrated from Abu Abdillah (as) who said:\n\"Commander of the Faithful (as) used to gather firewood, draw water, and sweep, while Sayiida Fatimah {s.a} used to grind, knead, and bake.\""
        ]
      }
